import pandas as pd
import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    ax = sns.countplot(x='key', data=data, order=data['key'].value_counts().index)
    ax.set_xticklabels(ax.get_xticklabels(), rotation=90)
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        ax.xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    plt.title("What is the most common type of cuisine offered by restaurants in the University District area?", wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()

    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()
